This is the project 1 for the course Embedded Interface Design.
The Project contains:
1.User Interface(.ui) file.
2.A python script which uses pyqt5 libraries to render UI.
How to Run the Code:Clone the git repository to your Raspberry Pi. Go to folder Project1 run the TemperatureQT_shuham.py script by typing in the terminal "python3 TemperatureQT_shubham.py" Then the GUI will Appear.
You can request the temperature, humidity,average temperature,average humidity and time data by clicking the fetch data button.
Plot button will plot the temperature and humidity data on a single graph. The graph will be ploteed only if the no of data points collected is greater than 10 and if not then an error message will be displayed
if the sensor is not connected and you try to fetch data an error will be displayed

